{"tid":1342171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搞還搞，唔好搞田同埋郊野地方","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:27:59.000Z","uid":262744,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d96e1296ee32e0a47a16280bacf2905cf2013aed","tid":1342171,"uid":262744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:18:27.000Z","msg":"鄉下好多地方都係啲人向地主租黎用<br />\n農業對於一個獨立既地區有幾咁重要<br />\n唔通焗住食鄰國啲毒菜<br />\n去搞田搞到啲農夫就唔好啦<br />\n同埋邊陲有好多有生態價值既地方<br />\n陣間唔小心燒埋又少啲天然資源<br />\n個啲發展商最鍾意燒地<br />\n總之社會唔可以冇咗呢啲根基<br />\n咁就求大家眼界瞄準啲"},{"pid":"119f3e2acbcdbef57408ca7f2425961865fff203","tid":1342171,"uid":262744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:20:52.000Z","msg":"而家又有翻P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsor for P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8d8f0c07a931bcfd66e49d52d2db8b60ed5fe5","tid":1342171,"uid":262744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:25:31.000Z","msg":"唔記得揀返時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之希望有緣人睇到啦"},{"pid":"a41b500e9e8cc1199e42bccf453ac4501535b9bf","tid":1342171,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:27:59.000Z","msg":"收到。<br />\n山墳有機嗎"}]}